<B><font size=3>Federal Securities Litigation Reform: Key Provisions And Future Questions, 
</FONT></B><font size=3 FACE="Times New Roman">by
Philip Allen</FONT>
<p>
Lacovara, Contemporary Legal Note. Lacovara examines the Private Securities Litigation Reform Act 
and outlines the issues involved in three major areas of the act: Title IReduction of litigation abuse, 
Title IIReduction of coercive settlements, and Title IIIAuditor disclosure of corporate fraud. The 
