<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/nationalreview/daily/nr112196.html 204.71.237.86 19970108091519 text/html 3180
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 09:15:37 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 22-Nov-96 23:13:06 GMT
