http://www.sbsc.org:80/nationalreview/daily/nr110296.html 204.71.237.86 19970108091629 text/html 4562
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 09:16:45 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 05-Nov-96 00:51:58 GMT
Content-length: 4375
Content-type: text/html
