<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000247-B042-40</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/townhall/FRC/faq/faq7.html 204.71.237.86 19970108091757 text/html 5031
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
